      "title": "Man with drugs, money worth Rs. 10Mn nabbed in Kotahena",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The STF has arrested a suspect in possession of 670g of ice and more than Rs. 1.45 million in cash during a raid in Kotahena last night.",
        "The STF said the street value of the seized drugs is more than Rs. 8 million.",
        "The suspect, a resident of Borella was handed over to the Kotahena Police."
